title: Skull Gang
text:
Skull Gang is an American hip hop collective formed in 2007, by Harlem rapper Juelz Santana. The group is best known for their projects Juelz Santana Presents Skull Gang: Takeover (2008) and Jim Jones & Skull Gang Present a Tribute to Bad Santa (2008). Skull Gang released their self-titled debut album on May 5, 2009. The "skull" in Skull Gang is an acronym which stands for "Street Kids United by Loyalty & Loot".
